1
00:00:22,589 --> 00:00:32,633
<i>[eerie music]</i>

2
00:00:32,633 --> 00:00:39,873
<i>[eerie music]</i>

3
00:00:39,940 --> 00:00:42,643
Is this true, my beloved queen?

4
00:00:42,676 --> 00:00:49,049
<i>It is... The Dream Mirror of</i>
<i>Pegasus's host will not look</i>
<i>like anyone else's.</i>

5
00:00:49,049 --> 00:00:52,886
<i>It will shine golden because of</i>
<i>the Golden Crystal.</i>

6
00:00:55,021 --> 00:00:57,624
<i>Do I make myself clear,</i>
<i>Zirconia?</i>

7
00:00:57,658 --> 00:01:01,061
<i>Look for the Golden Mirror.</i>

8
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:05,672
<i>Find and capture the one who</i>
<i>possesses the Dream Mirror that</i>
<i>shines like gold.</i>

9
00:01:05,706 --> 00:01:07,641
It will be done.

10
00:01:07,674 --> 00:01:12,245
There are very few beautiful
dreamers left who could
potentially be his host.

11
00:01:12,245 --> 00:01:15,716
So I assure you, Pegasus will
be in our hands very soon.

12
00:01:15,749 --> 00:01:18,251
Use those four girls wisely.

13
00:01:18,251 --> 00:01:21,321
But be careful to never
let your guard down.

14
00:01:23,323 --> 00:01:28,529
Yes, your majesty... lovely
Nehalennia, the True Queen
of the Moon!

15
00:01:33,033 --> 00:01:43,076
♪

16
