00:03:10,043 --> 00:03:13,614
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>"The Amazoness: Nightmare from</i>
<i>Behind the Mirrors"</i>

21
00:03:17,217 --> 00:03:18,451
‐Ooooh!
‐Ooooh!

22
00:03:20,486 --> 00:03:21,788
There. Perfect.

23
00:03:21,988 --> 00:03:23,156
Wow!

24
00:03:23,189 --> 00:03:25,025
<i>(Momo)</i>
<i>Hey Chibi‐Usa, did</i>
<i>you hear about Aki?</i>

25
00:03:25,058 --> 00:03:27,160
I sure did.

26
00:03:27,193 --> 00:03:30,564
She's so lucky. She got
to go see it with her
mom last week, right?

27
00:03:30,631 --> 00:03:34,134
Yeah. And of course she
said it was totally amazing.

28
00:03:34,167 --> 00:03:35,301
[groan]

29
00:03:35,335 --> 00:03:37,003
What is it? What's going on?

30
00:03:37,037 --> 00:03:39,039
It's about this!

31
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:41,041
<i>(Mamoru)</i>
<i>Huh?...The Dead Moon Circus?</i>

32
00:03:41,041 --> 00:03:43,409
<i>(Motoki)</i>
<i>It's that big circus tent</i>
<i>they put up downtown.</i>

33
00:03:43,476 --> 00:03:47,380
They asked us to put up ads for
it here in the Juban Shopping
District.

34
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,682
Oh...

35
00:03:48,715 --> 00:03:50,751
Oh, Mamo? I have a
question for you.

36
00:03:50,817 --> 00:03:56,389
Can you guess where your
favorite cute and adorable
little Chibi‐Usa wants to go
more than anywhere else?

37
00:03:56,389 --> 00:03:58,659
It starts with a "c"
and ends with an "s."

38
00:03:58,692 --> 00:04:00,193
[grunt]

39
00:04:00,226 --> 00:04:01,067
No way.

40
00:04:01,067 --> 00:04:02,736
Why not?

41
00:04:02,769 --> 00:04:06,206
Mamo, if you're taking someone
to the circus, it should be me,
and only me.

42
00:04:06,239 --> 00:04:10,176
Nobody has the right to come
between two people who are in
love.

43
00:04:10,210 --> 00:04:12,045
Wait, are you two
dating or something?

44
00:04:12,078 --> 00:04:15,248
Yup! In fact, we're planning
to get married someday.

45
00:04:15,281 --> 00:04:18,552
Uh, Usako? I think you're
wrinkling my shirt.

46
00:04:18,585 --> 00:04:20,020
Humph!

47
00:04:20,053 --> 00:04:22,122
Awww!

48
00:04:22,188 --> 00:04:25,626
Isn't it nice that your
big sister has such a
wonderful boyfriend?

49
00:04:25,692 --> 00:04:29,730
When you grow up, Momo, I'm sure
you'll find a man who's just as
crazy about <i>you.</i>

50
00:04:29,763 --> 00:04:31,565
Crazy?

51
00:04:31,598 --> 00:04:36,102
Really? So all I have to do is
wait till I grow up and I'll
have a wonderful boyfriend of my
own?

52
00:04:36,135 --> 00:04:40,440
Ohh, I can't wait to be a
grownup, then. It sounds fun!

53
00:04:40,473 --> 00:04:41,608
Huh?

54
00:04:42,275 --> 00:04:50,651
[happy giggling]

55
00:04:56,422 --> 00:04:59,492
I don't think I've seen
those girls before.

56
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:02,235
[gunfire]

57
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:10,310
Yeah! Vaporized him!

58
00:05:10,644 --> 00:05:12,078
[beeping]

59
00:05:12,112 --> 00:05:15,348
Girls, we need to go...

60
00:05:15,481 --> 00:05:17,350
We're being summoned.

61
00:05:24,024 --> 00:05:27,127
By the way, I think
you've got it wrong.

62
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,662
About what!?

63
00:05:28,695 --> 00:05:30,163
Being a grownup is dumb.

64
00:05:30,163 --> 00:05:34,000
They always have to get
permission to do anything,
even just to dream.

65
00:05:34,034 --> 00:05:39,105
Yeah, take it from me, becoming
an adult is nothing that any
sane kid would look forward to.

66
00:05:39,139 --> 00:05:43,644
In other words, refusing to grow
up and remaining a child forever
is really your best option.

67
00:05:43,677 --> 00:05:50,016
Always remember not to forget.
A child's dream is a dream they
should never get....

68
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:55,021
...Always remember not to
forget. A child's dream is a
dream they should never get...

69
00:05:55,055 --> 00:06:05,639
...Always remember not to
forget. A child's dream is a
dream they should never get.

70
00:06:06,673 --> 00:06:07,741
Huh???

71
00:06:07,808 --> 00:06:10,176
Whoa, kids these days sure
are cynical, aren't they?

72
00:06:10,210 --> 00:06:14,414
Not having a boyfriends who're
crazy about them must've
warped their personality.

73
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,149
Will you please stop?

74
00:06:21,522 --> 00:06:26,860
<i>A child's dream is a dream</i>
<i>they should never get. Always</i>
<i>remember not to forget...</i>

75
00:06:26,893 --> 00:06:33,233
...A child's dream is a dream
they should never get. Always
remember not to forget...

76
00:06:33,266 --> 00:06:39,172
...A child's dream is a dream
they should never get. Always
remember not to forget...

77
00:06:39,205 --> 00:06:43,510
...A child's dream is a dream
they should never get. Always
remember not to forget.

78
00:06:48,248 --> 00:06:51,718
Eureka! I've figured it out!
I've figured it out! I've
figured it <i>out!</i>

79
00:06:51,752 --> 00:06:56,356
Ah! It seems the young boy has
finally managed to figure it
out!

80
00:06:56,389 --> 00:07:00,727
He finally figured out that the
only time he's allowed to dream
is when he's sleeping.

81
00:07:00,761 --> 00:07:02,636
And then‐‐!
‐‐in the blink of an eye‐‐!

82
00:07:02,703 --> 00:07:06,607
‐‐that was the moment the young
boy grew up and became an adult.

83
00:07:06,607 --> 00:07:08,542
[squawk]

84
00:07:08,575 --> 00:07:11,444
That's when you find out
your beloved prince...

85
00:07:11,477 --> 00:07:13,246
‐...is really a toad in the
mirror.
‐...is really a toad in the
mirror.

86
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:17,918
The magic of dreams can make him
look like a prince, but his
voice is that of a toad.

87
00:07:17,951 --> 00:07:20,621
But can't you make your dreams
real‐‐

88
00:07:20,654 --> 00:07:23,123
‐‐even when you're‐‐
‐‐an adult?

89
00:07:23,156 --> 00:07:24,825
That's asking for
the impossible.

90
00:07:24,891 --> 00:07:27,594
That's a dream that will
never ever come true.

91
00:07:27,628 --> 00:07:29,930
So enjoy the fruit
while it's still ripe!

92
00:07:29,963 --> 00:07:32,232
Eat it up while
innocence remains!

93
00:07:32,265 --> 00:07:37,504
Always remember not to forget.
A child's dream is a dream they
should never get!

94
00:07:37,571 --> 00:07:42,776
...Always remember not to
forget. A child's dream is a
dream they should never get...

95
00:07:42,809 --> 00:07:48,649
...Always remember not to
forget. A child's dream is a
dream they should never get...

96
00:07:48,682 --> 00:07:54,755
...Always remember not to
forget. A child's dream is a
dream they should never get...

97
00:07:54,788 --> 00:07:59,860
Always remember not to forget.
A child's dream is a dream they
